WEBVTT

00:00.176 --> 00:03.112
♪♪

00:04.662 --> 00:07.364
<i>An alien named
the Beyonder took pieces of worlds,</i>

00:07.431 --> 00:10.233
<i>then mashed them together
to build Battleworld.</i>

00:10.369 --> 00:12.857
<i>The people
from those places, including the Avengers,</i>

00:12.924 --> 00:14.244
<i>were brought
to this world.</i>

00:14.312 --> 00:16.279
<i>The Beyonder calls this
his experiment.</i>

00:16.393 --> 00:18.533
<i>We call it twisted
and dangerous.</i>

00:18.997 --> 00:21.315
<i>After Loki joined our side,
we tried to use</i>

00:21.383 --> 00:23.948
<i>the Asgardian Bifrost
to send everyone home.</i>

00:24.065 --> 00:25.666
<i>It didn't work.</i>

00:26.459 --> 00:29.056
<i>The Beyonder retaliated by splitting
Hulk in two,</i>

00:29.151 --> 00:31.057
<i>then blasting them
both away.</i>

00:33.058 --> 00:35.666
<i>Now Loki and I
are rebuilding a new Bifrost</i>

00:35.799 --> 00:39.299
<i>so we can undo Battleworld and
end the Beyonder's experiment.</i>

00:40.111 --> 00:42.666
<i>What we need next
is to power the Bifrost.</i>

00:42.808 --> 00:44.775
<i>We need energy,
and lots of it.</i>

00:44.885 --> 00:47.236
<i>I'm thinking gamma energy.</i>

00:47.588 --> 00:50.424
<i>So we need our missing
gamma expert, Bruce Banner.</i>

00:50.492 --> 00:53.819
<i>Black Widow, Hulk trusts you.
If he's in one of his rages,</i>

00:53.887 --> 00:56.358
- <i>you can talk him down.
- And if she can't?</i>

00:56.426 --> 00:58.210
<i>That's why
you're going, Captain Marvel.</i>

00:58.277 --> 01:00.363
<i>Find the Hulk
and bring him home.</i>

